				\begin{document}$${{\boldsymbol{s}}}^{k}$$\end{document}sk improved as the number of scans per subject increased whereas the scan-level modularizations \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
